N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 22.12 - Filing of accounts

State Regulations

An account of proceedings, as specified under Banking Law, subsection 100-c(6), shall be filed within six months of the close of the
period covered by the account. Notes
